description:
Welcome all to the October's SWMobile Meetup.

Talk 1: An introduction to GraphQL - Daniel Leivers
Talk 2: Audience before app - Emily Perkins
Talk 3: Building Apps from "Features" using Flint framework as an example - Marc Palmer
Talk 4: Lessons making my first mobile game - Ben Byford

We'll be hosted by Cookpad who will also kindly be providing food and drink on the evening.

Doors will open at 18:30pm
- Food and drink will be available.
- Talks will start at 19:00 with interlude ~19:45
- We aim to be finished by 21:00

After the event, we'll move on to a near by pub to continue the discussions. 🍷

If you do have a talk that you'd like to present at a future meetup then please do get in touch via http://cfp.swmobile.org
title: October Meetup
